11
00:00:30,926 --> 00:00:33,906
We've learned a lot so far with this degree.

12
00:00:34,586 --> 00:00:37,956
Now, I'm hoping to use all of these
skills to help change the world.

13
00:00:37,956 --> 00:00:40,996
And I know that sounds really
cheesy, but just hear me out.

14
00:00:41,466 --> 00:00:42,916
Museums are magical places.

15
00:00:43,656 --> 00:00:45,836
Museums are the reason why
I studied what I studied,

16
00:00:46,066 --> 00:00:48,826
